40
00:03:51,620 --> 00:03:53,740
I'm really sorry.

41
00:03:54,780 --> 00:03:58,610
I won't let this happen again.

42
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:43,850
Did you come because you were worried about Woohyun?

43
00:04:43,850 --> 00:04:45,530
None of your business.

44
00:04:45,530 --> 00:04:46,900
I'm sorry.

45
00:04:46,900 --> 00:04:48,800
What are you planning?

46
