 I'll return your money. Sorry, Woohyun.

59
00:05:35,150 --> 00:05:37,850
Woohyun gave money?

60
00:05:39,450 --> 00:05:44,580
Seulbi acknowledged it, so now it's the end.

61
00:05:44,580 --> 00:05:47,450
No, no, no, no, no.

62
00:05:47,450 --> 00:05:49,720
We decide the end.

63
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:52,690
It's not the end,

64
00:05:52,690 --> 00:05:54,520
