82
00:07:28,820 --> 00:07:32,140
If you mess with the people I like,

83
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:34,040
I really...

84
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,400
won't be able to endure it.

85
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:37,830
Oh, Hwang Sungyeol,

86
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:39,990
Lee Seulbi said she liked you.

87
00:07:39,990 --> 00:07:42,090
Love triangle?

88
00:07:42,090 --> 00:07:44,430
