93
00:08:19,700 --> 00:08:20,990
Don't you feel resentful?

94
00:08:20,990 --> 00:08:25,210
At first, I did.  But you and Woohyun believe me,

95
00:08:25,210 --> 00:08:26,740
so it's fine.

96
00:08:26,740 --> 00:08:29,950
Don't get near Jaeseok. It's dangerous.

97
00:08:29,990 --> 00:08:32,590
But I feel really great today.

98
00:08:32,590 --> 00:08:35,470
I've always received from you.

99
00:08:35,470 --> 00:08:38,840
Even though today I just blocked for you.

100
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:42,050
Thanks for blocking.

101
00:08:42,050 --> 00:08:45,800
I still have a lot of debt for being luggage around you.

102
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:47,050
Debt?

103
00:08:47,050 --> 00:08:48,990
So I was wondering,

104
00:08:48,990 --> 00:08:52,240
