105
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:54,690
I'll do it all! Tell me everything!

106
00:08:54,690 --> 00:08:57,300
If you tell me sooner, that'll be better.

107
00:09:02,740 --> 00:09:06,600
What? Seulbi is not the one who stole it?

108
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:10,050
- Yena likes Woohyun, so I think she planned it. 
 - What?

109
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:16,350
It wasn't the first time that Chunsik was bullied by Jaeseok.

110
00:09:17,580 --> 00:09:20,990
Teacher, you really didn't know?

111
00:09:20,990 --> 00:09:22,480
Yeah...

112
00:09:23,910 --> 00:09:26,450
I...

113
00:09:26,450 --> 00:09:29,420
Seulbi took the blame for everyone.

114
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:32,760
I thought that you should know.

115
00:09:59,950 --> 00:10:02,860
What? Am I invisible?

116
00:10:02,860 --> 00:10:06,720
Why's he acting like that?

117
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:11,160
This is an expensive dress, but you didn't notice me?

118
00:10:12,390 --> 00:10:18,130
Ah, acting like you're not interested?

119
00:10:18,130 --> 00:10:22,210
It's not working because you're learning how to date through reading.

120
00:10:30,030 --> 00:10:38,990

121
00:10:43,130 --> 00:10:45,160
Mind your own business.

122
00:10:46,130 --> 00:10:48,020
What did I do?

123
00:10:48,020 --> 00:10:52,450
Why? Do you want to confess your guilt as well?

124
00:10:52,450 --> 00:10:55,000
I'm watching over you.

125
00:10:59,130 --> 00:11:00,900
Seulbi!

126
00:11:01,950 --> 00:11:03,720
Lee Seulbi!

127
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:10,600
You're giving Woohyun your notes, too?

128
00:11:11,540 --> 00:11:14,450
He's building a wall with studying, he probably doesn't need it. Right?

129
00:11:14,450 --> 00:11:16,230
That's why he needs it more.

130
00:11:16,230 --> 00:11:18,720
It's because he doesn't study. If he does, he'll do well.

131
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:22,000
It must be encouraging to have you by his side.

132
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:26,580
No. He always gets into trouble when he's with me.

133
00:11:26,580 --> 00:11:28,530
There's nothing I can do.

134
00:11:28,530 --> 00:11:31,990
A true friend always stays by your side.

135
00:11:31,990 --> 00:11:34,260
That sounds like a really good quote.

136
00:11:34,260 --> 00:11:37,980
Woohyun has a smart friend like you,

137
00:11:37,980 --> 00:11:40,140
so he must be really happy.

138
00:11:42,130 --> 00:11:44,140
What's that? Were you really talking about me?

139
00:11:44,140 --> 00:11:47,190
You're not a tiger. A mouse or a cat fits you more.

140
00:11:47,190 --> 00:11:48,950
What?

141
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:53,530
Your true friend Sungyeol is giving you this.

142
00:11:53,530 --> 00:11:56,280
A true friend?

143
00:11:56,280 --> 00:12:00,390
I can't even eat this, but why?

144
00:12:00,390 --> 00:12:04,460
- You know you're thankful. 
 - Then eat it.

145
00:12:04,460 --> 00:12:06,940
Change into something to eat!

146
00:12:09,900 --> 00:12:13,590
Next time, I suggest you bring it with something to eat.

147
00:12:13,590 --> 00:12:15,480
Let's go to class.

148
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:17,490
I'll be back.

149
00:12:22,270 --> 00:12:25,040
Why are they walking so close to each other?

150
00:12:26,040 --> 00:12:28,360
Fall down, zap!

151
00:12:31,570 --> 00:12:33,190
What?

152
00:12:33,990 --> 00:12:36,430
Hello... 
 - Okay.

153
00:12:47,160 --> 00:12:50,400
Really, why is he like that?!

154
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:52,290
This is so expensive though...

155
00:12:52,290 --> 00:12:56,420
- You feel really curious and annoyed, right? 
 - What?

156
00:12:56,420 --> 00:12:59,740
It'll appear soon.

157
00:12:59,740 --> 00:13:02,260
What are you imagining?

158
00:13:02,260 --> 00:13:08,030
The feeling of someone stealing my expired bread!

159
00:13:09,380 --> 00:13:13,670
The bread that goes over the expiration date spoils in no time.

160
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:16,990
It rots real soon!

161
00:13:16,990 --> 00:13:20,710
Teacher Choi! My expiration date is still far away!

162
00:13:20,710 --> 00:13:24,620
I'm still good. It's just that I got divorced once.

163
00:13:29,490 --> 00:13:32,200
Are you here to see Shin Woohyun?

164
00:13:35,430 --> 00:13:38,090
I'm so jealous.

165
00:13:43,330 --> 00:13:46,270
Ko Chunsik, you got something to say to me?

166
00:13:46,270 --> 00:13:49,140
No. Just because.

167
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:53,540
You? Did you come to write a letter of apology?

168
00:13:54,650 --> 00:13:56,020
Good luck.

169
00:13:56,020 --> 00:13:58,000
Do you not get a grasp of the situation?

170
00:13:58,000 --> 00:14:01,620
I'm the victim and you're the offender.

171
00:14:01,620 --> 00:14:04,550
I'll reveal your wrongdoings. Just wait.

172
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:07,560
- Don't you know Lee Seulbi confessed to being the thief? 
 - What?

173
00:14:07,560 --> 00:14:10,620
It was fun to see her apologize so earnestly.

174
00:14:10,620 --> 00:14:13,770
You must regret not seeing it because you were here.

175
00:14:13,770 --> 00:14:15,340
It's your doing.

176
00:14:15,340 --> 00:14:18,900
Oh! You're smart.

177
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:23,350
Did you call me?

178
00:14:25,590 --> 00:14:29,330
Shin Woohyun, aren't you on probation?

179
00:14:32,780 --> 00:14:39,750
Jaeseok, I'm tired of seeing your face everywhere.

180
00:14:39,750 --> 00:14:41,620
Go.

181
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:56,040
Is it a poem? "Lee Seulbi is innocent."

182
00:14:56,040 --> 00:15:00,080
Ah. Lee Seulbi did not steal it.

183
00:15:00,950 --> 00:15:03,200
She stole it, Lee Seulbi.

184
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:05,280
That's not it.

185
00:15:05,280 --> 00:15:08,810
Your heart.

186
00:15:08,810 --> 00:15:10,800
Do you feel wronged?

187
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:12,610
Huh?

188
00:15:12,610 --> 00:15:17,670
Woohyun, this thing called life is usually unfair.

189
00:15:17,670 --> 00:15:21,090
It's easier to recognize that and accept it.

190
00:15:28,810 --> 00:15:31,030
He looked like a good person.

191
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:34,900
Yes.

192
00:15:34,900 --> 00:15:37,890
Your son is good looking, too.

193
00:15:37,890 --> 00:15:39,430
Yes.

194
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:46,880
Thank you. Thanks to you, Woohyun wasn't expelled.

195
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:49,730
I just followed the policy.

196
00:15:49,730 --> 00:15:52,330
I won't ask you to live with him.

197
00:15:52,330 --> 00:15:54,900
Just watch over him from time to time.

198
00:15:55,850 --> 00:15:58,620
Where are you going?

199
00:15:58,620 --> 00:16:00,570
He and Sungyeol don't know.

200
00:16:00,570 --> 00:16:03,570
They think he's living in America with his dad.

201
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:13,420
