202
00:16:15,230 --> 00:16:19,030
Woohyun is your biological son.

203
00:16:20,540 --> 00:16:23,240
I told you to transfer schools.

204
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:25,400
Getting into trouble, and doing that.

205
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:29,870
Why? Does he not stack up well against your good-student son?

206
00:16:29,870 --> 00:16:34,100
Are you worried because he's good friends with your son?

207
00:16:36,090 --> 00:16:39,410
