208
00:16:39,410 --> 00:16:44,200
Do you think our Woohyun gets into trouble anywhere with anyone?

209
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:47,480
Our Woohyun is not like that.

210
00:16:49,850 --> 00:16:52,040
It's not like I'm asking you to raise him.

211
00:16:52,040 --> 00:16:54,780
I'm just asking you to watch over him from time to time.

212
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:57,720
Can you really not do it?

213
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,520
Yes.

214
00:16:59,520 --> 00:17:02,590
Yeah? Then...

215
00:17:02,590 --> 00:17:06,070
I'm going to tell your husband and your son

216
00:17:06,070 --> 00:17:08,640
