217
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:10,430
- Mother. 
 - What?

218
00:17:10,430 --> 00:17:13,350
Are you getting a divorce if that's revealed?

219
00:17:13,350 --> 00:17:15,210
Well, that's even better.

220
00:17:15,210 --> 00:17:18,670
If you get divorced, you can live with Woohyun.

221
00:17:19,650 --> 00:17:21,540
Get divorced again?

222
00:17:21,540 --> 00:17:25,830
