223
00:17:25,830 --> 00:17:28,200
And you want me to live with Woohyun?

224
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:30,920
You told me to leave since you would take good care of Woohyun.

225
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:34,030
I'm now about to live my own life.

226
00:17:37,490 --> 00:17:39,670
Don't come to see me again.

227
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,800
Hey! Hey!

228
00:17:42,800 --> 00:17:45,170
My goodness.

229
00:17:45,170 --> 00:17:49,130
Woohyun and I are so pitiful.

230
00:17:51,100 --> 00:17:55,200
My goodness. My Woohyun, that poor thing.

231
00:17:57,600 --> 00:17:59,700
Why are you apologizing when it's not even your business?

232
00:17:59,790 --> 00:18:01,710
Why did you give Yena money?

233
00:18:01,740 --> 00:18:03,180
That's not your business.

234
00:18:03,490 --> 00:18:06,130
I'm not acknowledging that,

235
00:18:06,380 --> 00:18:08,250
I just don't like being dirty and cheap.

236
00:18:08,260 --> 00:18:10,410
And I don't like it when you're having a hard time.

237
00:18:11,950 --> 00:18:13,110
I'm fine.

238
00:18:13,410 --> 00:18:16,030
