239
00:18:16,030 --> 00:18:18,700
I totally trust you. You totally trust me, right?

240
00:18:18,900 --> 00:18:20,000
So everything's fine now.

241
00:18:24,100 --> 00:18:27,040
Oh, my arm is so sore from writing the apology letter.

242
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:29,230
Why does my arm hurt so much?

243
00:18:30,060 --> 00:18:33,110
What kind of door is an apology letter? (wordplay)

244
00:18:33,940 --> 00:18:36,430
