245
00:18:41,600 --> 00:18:43,000
Oh, that feels nice.

246
00:18:43,320 --> 00:18:45,200
And there, too.

247
00:18:47,600 --> 00:18:49,300
So nice!

248
00:18:53,150 --> 00:18:55,180
