249
00:18:56,760 --> 00:18:58,580
You don't use your left hand!

250
00:18:59,170 --> 00:19:00,720
You're smart.

251
00:19:01,470 --> 00:19:03,330
After you're done eating, you have to come somewhere with me.

252
00:19:03,490 --> 00:19:05,560
If you don't go, you'll regret it.

253
00:19:07,550 --> 00:19:10,150
♫ If you wanna be my love...  ♫

