00:19:16,700 --> 00:19:18,200
I like this.

255
00:19:18,440 --> 00:19:19,840
The same thing twice?

256
00:19:20,530 --> 00:19:23,040
Ah! I saw it in a drama.

257
00:19:23,100 --> 00:19:23,900
It's a couple t-shirt!

258
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:26,200
Why are you explaining it so nicely?

259
00:19:26,550 --> 00:19:28,170
Is this okay?

260
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:37,600
Oh, it looks nice!

261
00:19:38,300 --> 00:19:39,700
Yeah.

262
00:19:43,860 --> 00:19:45,530
Let's buy grandma's, too.

263
00:19:45,550 --> 00:19:46,950
Should we?

264
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:57,900
Does it taste good?

265
00:19:58,450 --> 00:20:01,230
