00:38:45,900 --> 00:38:49,340
 While humans are afraid of dying,

508
00:38:49,340 --> 00:38:56,830
 I think I know why they talk during funerals.

509
00:38:56,830 --> 00:39:01,450
 They want to support each other's sadness,

510
00:39:01,450 --> 00:39:08,140
 and keep the memories of the deceased human.

511
00:39:08,200 --> 00:39:11,400
 That's why it's even more sad.

512
00:39:20,420 --> 00:39:22,470
Why are you guys here?

513
00:39:22,470 --> 00:39:25,170
You're not allowed here.

514
00:39:25,170 --> 00:39:32,140
My dad, he doesn't usually go to events, but

515
00:39:32,140 --> 00:39:35,810
he said I'll become a man if I go to a funeral...

516
00:39:35,810 --> 00:39:37,760
You came well.

517
00:39:37,800 --> 00:39:39,700
Come on in.

518
00:39:41,060 --> 00:39:43,100
Why are you pushing me?

519
00:40:25,630 --> 00:40:27,680
Honey!

520
00:40:32,020 --> 00:40:33,220
Why are you here?

521
00:40:33,220 --> 00:40:35,570
Sungyeol came.

522
00:40:35,570 --> 00:40:41,720
There are many things to organize, but since his parents aren't here, it will be hard for Woohyun.

523
00:40:41,720 --> 00:40:44,660
Honey, are you okay?

524
00:40:44,660 --> 00:40:47,520
Your face looks a little pale.

525
00:40:47,520 --> 00:40:49,370
I'm fine.

526
00:40:49,370 --> 00:40:53,920
The teachers are here, so I should probably go to them.

527
00:40:53,920 --> 00:40:56,560
Oh, yeah, go on in.

528
00:40:58,870 --> 00:41:03,360
Excuse me? You're Woohyun's mother.

529
00:41:03,360 --> 00:41:07,650
It's been a long time. Where have you been?

530
00:41:07,650 --> 00:41:11,220
I think you got the wrong person.

531
00:41:13,100 --> 00:41:15,190
No...

532
00:41:15,190 --> 00:41:17,700
I think I was right...

533
00:41:18,940 --> 00:41:22,610
- Yeah, Mom. 
 -  Do you have time over the weekend?

